title: What is the difference between Dutch House, Dirty Dutch, and Melbourne Bounce? - Quora

response.answer_text: Not much, they are all nasty folks. All three were in the St. Valentine’s Day massacre, as shooters, and all 3 ended up in bad shape under mysterious circumstances. Dirty Dutch was found in a barrel in the Colorado river, Dutch House was found tied to a wild horse and dragged for approximately 4 days, and Melbourne Bounce wound up turning states’ evidence and was moved to Michigan under the Witness Protection act, where he was renamed”Foo Foo La Fitte” and posed as a woman for 35 years.
